## 3. FeatureFlagService (NCDS037)

### 3.1 Arquitetura
```python
class FeatureFlagService:
    def __init__(self, cache_ttl=3600):
        self.cache: Dict[str, Tuple[bool, float]] = {}  # flag  (value, expire_at)
        self.cache_ttl = cache_ttl
        
    def is_enabled(self, flag: str, user_id: Optional[str] = None) -> bool:
        """Retorna True se flag habilitada (com cache)."""
        
    def refresh(self, flag: str):
        """Fora refresh da flag (chama Growthbook ou configurao local)."""
```

### 3.2 Configurao YAML (exemplo)
```yaml
# neocortex_config.yaml
feature_flags:
  # Flags locais (sobrescrevem Growthbook)
  mcp_wqueue: false
  persistent_worker: true
  confidence_review: false
  channel_notifications: false
  push_notifications: true
  proactive_mode: false
  coordinator_mode: false
  
  # Rollout percentual (ex.: 30% dos usurios)
  beta_features:
    percentage: 30
    user_attribute: "user_id"
    
  # Cache TTL (segundos)
  cache_ttl: 3600
```

### 3.3 Uso no Cdigo
